column5: Any guys here fish the Rainy River at Baudette? Are the Walleyes biting now? It's actually pretty crazy, the mild weather has caused the rainy river in front of my apartment to completely open up, it looks like November!

Hello went to sportsmans lodge January 15 thru the 18th Ice fished in Traverse bay caught 51 walleye and Sauger the biggest was only 16 inches very light bite about 6 in off the bottom with a purple or pink jig combination 1/16 oz weight tipped with a fathead ice thick ness about 14 inches 2miles out from shore very little snow on the ice ..
